Summary: OpenOffice.org Office Suite
Name: ooo
Version: @VERSION@
Vendor: Ximian, Inc.
Release: @RPM_RELEASE@
Provides: ooo-@VERSION@
Obsoletes: openoffice openoffice-libs openoffice-i18n
Conflicts: openoffice openoffice-libs openoffice-i18n
Requires: gtk2 gnome-vfs2 unzip gnome-cups-manager
